{"TopicId":87661,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"How do you let your kerbals have fun?","CreatedByName":"CG_Kerbin","CreatedById":117777,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-17T16:16:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"CG_Kerbin","CreatedById":117777,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-17T16:16:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EOnce in a while kerbals have to take a break I want to know how do you let them do this? Do you stop them from going on a rocket to their death or put on a huge party? big or small put it here. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E Thank you!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022459\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=UUYT2CcYN2OnEcaUcIBuroFw\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis is my attempt (sorry I know the video sucks) I\u0027d love to see what you guys do!\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-10-18T07:24:53Z\u0022 title=\u002210/18/2014 07:24  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 18, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by CG_Kerbin\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tg626","CreatedById":112361,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-17T16:36:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/8Gv0H-vPoDc?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u