s face. They all enjoy that.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stratzenblitz75","CreatedById":108287,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-17T19:59:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe only \u0022fun\u0022 my Kerbals experience is the relief that they weren\u0027t chosen to test my new 99.9% likely to fail contraption.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CG_Kerbin","CreatedById":117777,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-17T20:48:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stratzenblitz75\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Stratzenblitz75\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThe only \u0022fun\u0022 my Kerbals experience is the relief that they weren\u0027t chosen to test my new 99.9% likely to fail contraption.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E pretty much the same for me but 99.99% chance to fail XD\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CG_Kerbin","CreatedById":117777,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-18T06:29:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022worir4\u0022 data-cite=\u0022worir4\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EBy fun you mean 50Gs right? Or perhaps several explosions on a Kerbals face. They all enjoy that.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThey sure do!!!! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-18T06:45:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CG_Kerbin\u0022 data-cite=\u0022CG_Kerbin\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EOnce in a \u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:line-through;\u0022\u003Ewill\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Ewhile\u003C/strong\u003E \u003Cspan style=\u0022text-decoration:line-through;\u0022\u003Ek\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EK\u003C/strong\u003Eerbals have to take a break\u003Cstrong\