Id":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-18T17:17:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMy Kerbals are too busy to have any fun. They spend all the time going through long checklists and doing exactly what CAPCOM tells them to do. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBut returning home in one piece is a thing worth all the hassle.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CG_Kerbin","CreatedById":117777,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-19T06:59:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022WildLynx\u0022 data-cite=\u0022WildLynx\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EMy Kerbals are too busy to have any fun. They spend all the time going through long checklists and doing exactly what CAPCOM tells them to do. \u003Cp\u003EBut returning home in one piece is a thing worth all the hassle.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Emy kerbals get one break ever and its a 15mins lunch break XD\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Destroyer","CreatedById":36109,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-10-19T07:06:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI put them on chairswings.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=UUCdJxri7j0e4u8oG2FbNbWw\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"}]}